Package structures.commons

Contains all of the shared interfaces throughout the library.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataStructure<K>
    Generic interface for any data structure in this library.
    Pair<K,V>
    Key-value pair object for use in Objects such as Maps and Trees.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataStructure.EmptyDataStructureException
    Exception that is throw when an operation takes places that requires the DataStructure to be non-empty, but its empty.

Package structures.commons Description

Contains all of the shared interfaces throughout the library. By convention, this library will not include concrete classes. This is in the effort to avoid tight coupling of classes, and allowing implementing classes to handle the implementation. Essentially, this is a library of interfaces that specify common behavior.
